@startuml Post_Creation_Sequence_Detailed
!theme blueprint
title Post Creation System - Complete User Flow & Database Integration

actor User as U
participant "UI Components\n(Sidebar/BottomBar)" as UI
participant "NewPost Modal\n(Vue Component)" as NP
participant "Posts Store\n(Pinia State)" as PS
participant "API Client\n(HTTP Service)" as API
participant "Backend API\n(api.localtest.me:3001)" as BE
database "PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as DB

== Phase 1: Post Creation Initiation ==
U -> UI: 1. Click "Create Post" button
note right: User initiates post creation from sidebar or mobile bottom bar

UI -> UI: 2. Open NewPost modal dialog
UI -> NP: 3. Mount NewPost component with isOpen=true
NP -> NP: 4. Initialize form state & detect screen size
note right
**Component Initialization:**
const formData = ref<CreatePostRequest>({
  title: '',
  content: '',
  game_id: '',
  post_type: 'general',
  tags: [],
  visibility: 'public'
});
end note

== Phase 2: Content Loading ==
NP -> API: 5. fetchGameCategories()
note right
**API Request:**
- URL: /api/game-categories
- Method: GET
- Purpose: Populate game selection dropdown
end note

API -> BE: 6. GET /api/game-categories
BE -> DB: 7. SELECT game categories

DB --> BE: 8. Game categories data
BE --> API: 9. JSON response with categories
note right
**Response Format:**
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "category-uuid",
      "game_name": "Valorant",
      "created_at": "2025-08-01T10:00:00Z"
    }
  ]
}
end note

API --> NP: 10. Categories array
NP -> NP: 11. Populate dropdown options
NP -> U: 12. Display form with loaded categories

== Phase 3: User Form Interaction ==
U -> NP: 13. Fill in post details

NP -> NP: 14. Real-time form validation
note right
**Frontend Validation:**
const isFormValid = computed(() => {
  return !!(
    formData.value.title.trim() &&
    formData.value.content.trim() &&
    formData.value.title.length <= 255
  );
});
**Validation Rules:**
- Title and content required
- Character limits enforced
- Real-time feedback
end note

U -> NP: 15. Click "Create Post" button
NP -> NP: 16. Final form validation & processing
note right
**Submit Processing:**
const tagsArray = tagsInput.value
  .split(',')
  .map(tag => tag.trim())
  .filter(tag => tag.length > 0);

formData.value.tags = tagsArray;
end note

== Phase 4: Authentication & Data Submission ==
NP -> PS: 17. createPost(formData)
PS -> PS: 18. Authentication validation
note right
**Authentication Check:**
const userStore = useUserStore();
if (!userStore.isAuthenticated || !userStore.user) {
  throw new Error('User must be authenticated to create posts');
}
end note

PS -> PS: 19. Transform data for backend API
note right
**Data Transformation:**
const backendData = {
  title: postData.title,
  content: postData.content,
  game_id: postData.game_id?.trim() || undefined,
  post_type: postData.post_type || 'Discussion',
  tags: postData.tags || [],
  visibility: postData.visibility || 'public',
  published: true
};
end note

PS -> API: 20. createPost(backendData)
API -> BE: 21. POST /api/posts
note right
**API Request Details:**
- URL: /api/posts
- Method: POST
- Headers: Content-Type application/json
- Credentials: include (session cookie)
- Body: Transformed post data
end note

== Phase 5: Backend Authentication & Validation ==
BE -> BE: 22. Extract and validate session
note right
**Multi-Source Authentication:**
let sessionId = 
  headers.authorization?.substring(7) ||      // Bearer token
  headers['x-session-id'] ||                  // Session header
  cookie.astral_session?.value;              // Session cookie
**Session Priority:**
1. Authorization Bearer header
2. X-Session-ID header  
3. astral_session cookie
end note

BE -> DB: 23. Validate session & get user
note right
**Validation Checks:**
- Session exists in database
- Session not expired
- Associated user exists
- Provider information available
end note

DB --> BE: 24. Session data with user info

alt Session Valid & User Authenticated
    BE -> BE: 25. Validate and sanitize post data
    note right
    **Backend Validation:**
    const validation = {
      title: sanitizeTitle(body.title),
      content: sanitizeContent(body.content),
      gameId: validateUUID(body.game_id),
      postType: validatePostType(body.post_type),
      tags: validateTags(body.tags),
      visibility: validateVisibility(body.visibility)
    };
    end note

    == Phase 6: Database Post Creation ==
    BE -> DB: 26. INSERT new post record

    DB -> DB: 27. Execute database triggers

    DB --> BE: 28. New post data with generated fields
    note right
    **Created Post Response:**
    {
      "id": "new-post-uuid",
      "created_at": "2025-08-04T12:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-08-04T12:00:00Z"
    }
    end note

    BE --> API: 29. Success response with post data
    note right
    **API Success Response:**
    {
      "success": true,
      "message": "Post created successfully",
      "data": {
        "id": "new-post-uuid",
        "created_at": "2025-08-04T12:00:00Z",
        "updated_at": "2025-08-04T12:00:00Z"
      }
    }
    end note

    API --> PS: 30. Post creation confirmation
    
    == Phase 7: Post-Creation Updates ==
    PS -> API: 31. fetchPosts() - Refresh post list
    note right
    **Post List Refresh:**
    await this.fetchPosts({ 
      page: 1, 
      ...this.currentFilter 
    });
    end note

    API -> BE: 32. GET /api/posts with current filters
    BE -> DB: 33. SELECT posts with new post included
    DB --> BE: 34. Updated posts array
    BE --> API: 35. Refreshed posts response
    API --> PS: 36. Updated posts data
    PS -> PS: 37. Update local posts state
    PS --> NP: 38. Post creation success
    NP -> NP: 39. Reset form & close modal
    NP -> UI: 40. Emit 'created' event with new post
    UI -> U: 41. Show success feedback & updated post list
    note right
    **User Experience:**
    - Immediate success feedback
    - Form automatically cleared
    - Modal closes smoothly
    - New post visible in feed
    - No page refresh required
    end note

else Session Invalid or Expired
    BE --> API: 29b. 401 Unauthorized
    note right
    **Authentication Error:**
    {
      "success": false,
      "message": "Authentication required",
      "error": "Invalid or expired session"
    }
    end note

    API --> PS: 30b. Authentication error
    PS -> NP: 31b. Display authentication error
    NP -> U: 32b. Show "Please log in" message
    note right
    **Error Recovery:**
    - Clear invalid session
    - Redirect to login page
    - Preserve form data if possible
    - Resume after authentication
    end note
end

== Phase 8: Error Handling Scenarios ==
alt Form Validation Error
    NP -> NP: 25b. Client-side validation failure
    NP -> U: 26b. Display validation error messages
    note right
    **Validation Errors:**
    - "Title is required"
    - "Content cannot be empty"
    - "Title too long (max 255 characters)"
    - Real-time error highlighting
    end note
end

alt Network or Server Error
    API --> PS: 30c. Network/server error
    PS -> NP: 31c. Display error message
    NP -> U: 32c. Show "Try again" with retry option
    note right
    **Error Types:**
    - Network connectivity issues
    - Server 500 errors
    - Database connection problems
    - Timeout errors
    **Recovery Options:**
    - Retry button
    - Save draft locally
    - Error reporting
    end note
end

alt Database Constraint Error
    DB --> BE: 28b. Constraint violation error
    BE --> API: 29c. 422 Validation Error
    API --> PS: 30d. Data validation error
    PS -> NP: 31d. Display specific field errors
    NP -> U: 32d. Show field-specific error messages
    note right
    **Constraint Errors:**
    - Invalid game_id foreign key
    - Title length violation
    - Content type mismatch
    - Tag format errors
    **User Guidance:**
    - Specific field highlighting
    - Suggested corrections
    - Format examples
    end note
end

@enduml
